{
  "script_id": "ear-clipping",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "计算机眼里，最好处理的图形是三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "可现实中的图形往往是复杂的多边形，甚至带着凹进去的角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "于是我们想：能不能把任意简单多边形，切成若干个三角形？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.09,
      "size": 17424,
      "text": "关键是找到多边形上的\"耳朵\"。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.09,
      "size": 49392,
      "text": "一只耳朵，是一个凸出去的顶点，它和相邻两点连成的三角形，内部不含任何其他顶点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "这样的三角形可以放心切下，不会切到多边形外面去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "clip",
      "line_id": "clip-1",
      "filename": "clip-clip-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/clip-clip-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "切下一只耳朵，多边形就少了一个顶点，剩下的仍是简单多边形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "clip",
      "line_id": "clip-2",
      "filename": "clip-clip-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/clip-clip-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.55,
      "size": 40752,
      "text": "在剩下的图形上继续找耳朵、继续切，像削苹果皮一样一步步进行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "clip",
      "line_id": "clip-3",
      "filename": "clip-clip-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/clip-clip-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "直到最后只剩一个三角形，整个多边形就被完全剖分了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-1",
      "filename": "count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "数学上可以证明，任何简单多边形都至少有两只耳朵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-2",
      "filename": "count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "一个 n 条边的多边形，最终恰好被切成 n 减 2 个三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "点击单步按钮，每按一次就切下一只耳朵，看三角形逐个出现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "换成五角星试试，凹角会让某些顶点暂时当不了耳朵。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "耳切法用一个简单的贪心规则，把复杂多边形化整为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "它是计算机图形学里三角化的经典算法，简单又可靠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "ear-clipping",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/ear-clipping/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "从一只耳朵到满屏三角，这就是几何的巧思，我们下次再见！"
    }
